        <updateDate>2006-05-24T17:34:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Consumer Cancellation Fairness Act - Directs the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) to require subscription service providers to allow subscribers to cancel service the same way they subscribed to such service.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
